title: Washington, Cam Newton, Lakers, NBA bubble
itunes:title: Washington, Cam Newton, Lakers, NBA bubble
description:
Filling in for Colin, Doug Gottlieb discusses his thoughts on the Washington Redskins possibly changing their name, Cam Newton wanting respect over money, and why the Lakers don't have an extra advantage over teams playing in the bubble. Guests include Antonio Daniels, and John Middlekauff.
